<% content_for :title, "Wisdom From You - A Letter" %>

<body class="bg-[#121212] text-[#e0e0e0] font-serif leading-relaxed m-0 p-0 flex justify-center items-center min-h-screen" style="text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.1);">
    <div class="max-w-[800px] p-10 bg-[rgba(18,18,18,0.8)] rounded-2xl shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,255,255,0.1)] mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-[#4a90e2] text-4xl text-center mb-8">Wisdom From You - A Letter</h1>
        

        <p class="mb-5 text-lg opacity-90 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300">All the wisdom we know, from what we call the divine to the practical, has come through humanity.</p>
        

        <p class="mb-5 text-lg opacity-90 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300">The me's and you's that have come before and are yet to come.</p>
        

        <p class="question mb-5 text-lg font-bold text-[#03dac6]">What would my life and your life look like if we could always tap into the wisdom that moves through us?</p>
        

        <p class="mb-5 text-lg opacity-90 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300">This software and art form is the movement towards finding that answer:</p>
        

        <p class="question mb-5 text-lg font-bold text-[#03dac6]">Could we change ourselves, and therefore our worlds, by constantly asking ourselves the right questions?</p>
        

        <p class="mb-5 text-lg opacity-90 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300">I am Ikraam, the first user here, I hope you will join me.</p>
        

        <div class="signature text-right italic mt-10">- Ikraam</div>
        



        <div class="post-thought mt-16 pt-5 border-t border-[#4a90e2]">
            <p class="mb-5 text-lg opacity-90 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"><strong>Post Thought:</strong></p>
            <p class="mb-5 text-lg opacity-90 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300">This platform is a question and it will transform me and you. We are its creation as we create it.</p>
            


            <p class="mb-5 text-lg opacity-90 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300">Here is a meta-question for you and me:</p>
            <p class="question mb-5 text-lg font-bold text-[#03dac6]">Is the point of a question to find an answer or is to experience the process of answering it?</p>
        </div>
    </div>


</body>